ly those to whom it has been given."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 13:11","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":11,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Co 7:7","book":"1Co","chapter":7,"verse":7,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 13:11","book":"Mat","chapter":13,"verse":11},{"label":"1Co 7:7","book":"1Co","chapter":7,"verse":7}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:19:12","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"For there are eunuchs who were born that way from their mother’s womb, there are eunuchs who were made by men, and there are eunuchs who have made themselves that way because of the kingdom of heaven. The one who is able to accept it should accept it.”"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:19:13","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Then little children were brought to Jesus for him to place his hands on them and pray, but the disciples rebuked them. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 10:13–16","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":13,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 18:15–17","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":15,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 10:13–16","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":13},{"label":"Lk 18:15–17","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":15}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:19:14","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Jesus said, “Leave the little children alone, and don’t try to keep them from coming to me, because the kingdom of heaven belongs to such as these.”"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Lit heaven is of such ones"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 18:3","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"1Pt 2:2","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"text","text":" "}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mt 18:3","book":"Mat","chapter":18,"verse":3},{"label":"1Pt 2:2","book":"1Pe","chapter":2,"verse":2}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Lit heaven is of such ones"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:19:15","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"After placing his hands on them, he went on from there."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:19:16","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Just then someone came up and asked him, "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 10:17–30","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":17,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 10:25–28","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":25,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lk 18:18–30","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":18,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"text","text":" “Teacher, what good must I do to have eternal life?” "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mk 10:17","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":17,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jn 12:25","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":25,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ac 13:48","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":48,"letter":"f"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Mk 10:17–30","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":17},{"label":"Lk 10:25–28","book":"Luk","chapter":10,"verse":25},{"label":"Lk 18:18–30","book":"Luk","chapter":18,"verse":18},{"label":"Mk 10:17","book":"Mrk","chapter":10,"verse":17},{"label":"Jn 12:25","book":"Jhn","chapter":12,"verse":25},{"label":"Ac 13:48","book":"Act","chapter":13,"verse":48}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:19:17","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Why do you ask me about what is good?”"},{"kind":"footnote","marker":1,"text":"Other mss read “Why do you call me good?”"},{"kind":"text","text":" he said to him. “There is only one who is good."},{"kind":"footnote","marker":2,"text":"Other mss read “No one is good but one —God"},{"kind":"text","text":" If you want to enter into life, keep the commandments.”"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 18:5","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":5,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Neh 9:29","book":"Neh","chapter":9,"verse":29,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ezk 20:21","book":"Ezk","chapter":20,"verse":21,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Lv 18:5","book":"Lev","chapter":18,"verse":5},{"label":"Neh 9:29","book":"Neh","chapter":9,"verse":29},{"label":"Ezk 20:21","book":"Ezk","chapter":20,"verse":21}],"footnotes":[{"marker":1,"text":"Other mss read “Why do you call me good?”"},{"marker":2,"text":"Other mss read “No one is good but one —God"}]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:19:18","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"“Which ones?” he asked him."}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Mat:19:19","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"honor your father and your mother; and love your neighbor as yourself."},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 20:12–16","book":"Exo","chapter":20,"verse":12,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 19:18","book":"Lev","chapter":19,"verse":18,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 5:16","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":16,"letter":"c"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Ex 20:12","book":"Exo","chapter":20,"verse":12,"letter":"d"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Lv 19:18","book":"Lev","chapter":19,"verse":18,"letter":"e"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Dt 5:16","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":16,"letter":"f"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 5:43","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":43,"letter":"g"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Mt 22:39","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":39,"letter":"h"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Gl 5:14","book":"Gal","chapter":5,"verse":14,"letter":"i"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jms 2:8","book":"Jas","chapter":2,"verse":8,"letter":"j"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Ex 20:12–16","book":"Exo","chapter":20,"verse":12},{"label":"Lv 19:18","book":"Lev","chapter":19,"verse":18},{"label":"Dt 5:16","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":16},{"label":"Ex 20:12","book":"Exo","chapter":20,"verse":12},{"label":"Lv 19:18","book":"Lev","chapter":19,"verse":18},{"label":"Dt 5:16","book":"Deu","chapter":5,"verse":16},{"label":"Mt 5:43","book":"Mat","chapter":5,"verse":43},{"label":"Mt 22:39","book":"Mat","chapter":22,"verse":39},{"label":"Gl 5:14","book":"Gal","cha